ActFederal Public Sector Labour Relations Act
SubjectCanadian Food Agency - Professional Institute of the Public Service of Canada ** Collective Agreement **
PrecisOrder approving the ENTRY by the Canadian Food Inspection Agency into a COLLECTIVE AGREEMENT with the PROFESSIONAL INSTITUTE OF THE PUBLIC SERVICE OF CANADA that covers all employees of the Agency in the Veterinary Medicine (VM) Bargaining Unit, for the period beginning on October 1, 2018 and ending on September 30, 2022.
